{{Infobox brain|Name=布罗德曼45区|Latin=Area triangularis|Image=Brodmann area 45.png|Caption=|Image2=Brodmann Cytoarchitectonics 45.png|Caption2=|Artery=[[middle_cerebral_artery|middle cerebral artery]]|Vein=|Acronym=|part_of=[[额叶|额叶]]}}'''布罗德曼45区'''（英文：Brodmann area 45），简称'''BA45'''，是[[大脑皮质|大脑皮质]]的[[额叶|额叶]]的一个细胞结构分区<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Brodmann Area 45 - an overview|url=https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/neuroscience/brodmann-area-45|access-date=2022-05-05|work=ScienceDirect|language=en|archive-date=2021-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211030154949/https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/neuroscience/brodmann-area-45}}</ref>。它位于额叶的外侧部，[[布罗德曼44区|布罗德曼44区]]之前，[[布罗德曼9区|布罗德曼9区]]之下，与[[布罗德曼46区|布罗德曼46区]]之后<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=Area 45 of Brodmann|url=http://braininfo.rprc.washington.edu/centraldirectory.aspx?ID=2403|access-date=2022-05-05|work=[[华盛顿大学|华盛顿大学]]|language=en|archive-date=2021-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210414000439/http://braininfo.rprc.washington.edu/centraldirectory.aspx?ID=2403}}</ref>。

== 结构 ==
BA44的上界为[[额下沟|额下沟]]，后界为[[外侧沟|外侧沟]]的上升枝。BA45在深度上延伸到[[岛叶|岛叶]]之界。该区域亦称为[[额下回|额下回]]的'''三角部'''（Pars triangularis）。<ref name=":1" />

== 功能 ==
布罗德曼45区与布罗德曼44区一起组成[[布洛卡区|布洛卡区]]，与[[语言|语言]]，尤其是[[语义|语义]]的处理相关<ref name=":0" /><ref>{{Cite journal|title=The role of the left Brodmann's areas 44 and 45 in reading words and pseudowords|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/16310346/|last=Heim|first=Stefan|last2=Alter|first2=Kai|date=2005-12|journal=Brain Research. Cognitive Brain Research|issue=3|doi=10.1016/j.cogbrainres.2005.09.022|volume=25|pages=982–993|issn=0926-6410|pmid=16310346|last3=Ischebeck|first3=Anja K.|last4=Amunts|first4=Katrin|last5=Eickhoff|first5=Simon B.|last6=Mohlberg|first6=Hartmut|last7=Zilles|first7=Karl|last8=von Cramon|first8=D. Yves|last9=Friederici|first9=Angela D.|access-date=2022-05-05|archive-date=2021-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211104045158/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/16310346/}}</ref>。

布罗德曼45区的具体语言功能尚有争议。一些研究者认为它与语义获取（Semantic retrieval）和语义[[工作记忆|工作记忆]]有关<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Different roles of cytoarchitectonic BA 44 and BA 45 in phonological and semantic verbal fluency as revealed by dynamic causal modelling|url=https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S1053811909006806|last=Heim|first=Stefan|last2=Eickhoff|first2=Simon B.|date=2009-11-15|journal=NeuroImage|issue=3|doi=10.1016/j.neuroimage.2009.06.044|volume=48|pages=616–624|language=en|issn=1053-8119|last3=Amunts|first3=Katrin}}</ref>。另外一种观点认为，BA45不仅与语义相关，也参与选择与任务相关表示的表示<ref>{{Cite journal
 | author = Thompson-Schill ''et al.''
 | year = 1999
 | title = Effects of repetition and competition on activity of left prefrontal cortex during word generation
 | journal = [[Neuron_(journal)|Neuron]]
 | volume = 23
 | pages = 513–522
 | doi = 10.1016/S0896-6273(00)80804-1
}}</ref>。

